## RBAC（Role-Based）
```typescript
const PERMISSIONS = {
  ADMIN: ["users.*", "posts.*", "settings.*"],
  EDITOR: ["posts.read", "posts.write"],
  VIEWER: ["posts.read"]
};

function can(user, permission) {
  return PERMISSIONS[user.role].some(p =>
    p === permission || p === `${permission.split(".")[0]}.*`
  );
}
```

## ABAC（Attribute-Based）
```typescript
function canEditPost(user, post) {
  if (user.role === "admin") return true;
  if (post.author_id === user.id) return true;
  if (user.role === "editor" && post.status === "draft") return true;
  return false;
}
```

## Casl（JS）
```typescript
import { AbilityBuilder, Ability } from "@casl/ability";

function defineAbilitiesFor(user) {
  const { can, cannot, build } = new AbilityBuilder(Ability);

  if (user.role === "admin") {
    can("manage", "all");
  } else {
    can("read", "Post");
    can("update", "Post", { author_id: user.id });
  }

  return build();
}

// 用
const ability = defineAbilitiesFor(user);
if (ability.can("update", post)) { /* 允許 */ }
```

## Row Level Security（PG）
DB 層級權限：
```sql
ALTER TABLE posts ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;

CREATE POLICY "own_posts" ON posts
FOR ALL USING (author_id = auth.uid());

CREATE POLICY "admin_all" ON posts
FOR ALL USING (
  EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM users WHERE id = auth.uid() AND role = 'admin')
);
```

Supabase 內建。

## Multi-tenant

### 模式 1：Shared DB + tenant_id
```sql
CREATE TABLE posts (
  id UUID,
  tenant_id UUID,
  ...
);

-- RLS
CREATE POLICY "tenant_isolation" ON posts
FOR ALL USING (tenant_id = current_setting('app.tenant_id')::uuid);
```

### 模式 2：Schema per tenant
- 每 tenant 一個 schema
- 隔離強
- 管理複雜

### 模式 3：DB per tenant
- 最強隔離
- 成本高
- 適合企業客戶

## Middleware
```typescript
// Express
function requirePermission(permission) {
  return (req, res, next) => {
    if (!can(req.user, permission)) {
      return res.status(403).end();
    }
    next();
  };
}

app.delete("/posts/:id", requirePermission("posts.delete"), deletePost);
```

```typescript
// Next.js Middleware
export async function middleware(req) {
  const user = await getUser(req);
  if (req.nextUrl.pathname.startsWith("/admin") && user.role !== "admin") {
    return NextResponse.redirect("/");
  }
}
```

## IDOR 防護
永遠檢查擁有者：
```typescript
// ❌
app.get("/api/posts/:id", (req, res) => {
  return db.post.findUnique({ where: { id: req.params.id } });
});

// ✅
app.get("/api/posts/:id", async (req, res) => {
  const post = await db.post.findUnique({ where: { id: req.params.id } });
  if (post.author_id !== req.user.id && req.user.role !== "admin") {
    return res.status(403).end();
  }
  return post;
});
```

## 心法
- 永遠在 server 檢查（前端只是 UX）
- RBAC 起手、需要再 ABAC
- RLS 雙保險
- 永遠檢查 ownership

